file_content.text: You got us Astar Vox? Hah! Ulgo's not going to know what hit them!
House Teral needs friends like you if we're going to make it.
Thanks again. Give me a combat lesson sometime!
You hear about Jedi on the battlefield, but to actually see it... no wonder Ulgo's running for their lives.
Let me open the security doors; Lord Teral will want to see you right away. And... thank you. We could never have stopped them alone.
A Jedi? I can't believe--I thought those Ulgos had us pinned for sure.
Captain Theress, House Teral security. Thanks for coming out of nowhere.
It's not me I'm worried about.
I'm just here for Lord Teral.
I don't think this is over yet. For Ulgo, that was a pretty paltry force.
I think the real attack is still coming. Please, Master Jedi--we can't let those Ulgo monsters anywhere near the lord's family.
